OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782816485
OL,3,CBurnham refuses to take journalists'
OL,4,Cquestions after speech setting out
OL,5,Cvision
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has been accused of
OL,8,F"power without accountability" by
OL,9,Frefusing to take questions from
OL,10,Fjournalists following his first major
OL,11,Fspeech.
OL,13,FThe Makerfield MP, who is on course to
OL,14,Fbecome prime minister in three weeks'
OL,15,Ftime, was using a speech in Manchester
OL,16,Fto set out his vision for the country.
OL,18,FBut the senior Labour politician did
OL,19,Fnot follow the common practice of
OL,20,Ftaking questions from reporters
OL,21,Ffollowing the speech.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
