PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782816485
OL,3,CBurnham refuses to take journalists'
OL,4,Cquestions after speech setting out
OL,5,Cvision
OL,7,FBurnham is expected to succeed Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer as head of the party on
OL,9,F17 July and become prime minister on
OL,10,F20 July.
OL,12,FThis will be after MPs leave
OL,13,FWestminster for the summer, meaning he
OL,14,Fwill not face Prime Minister's
OL,15,FQuestions in the Commons until
OL,16,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782816485
OL,3,CBurnham refuses to take journalists'
OL,4,Cquestions after speech setting out
OL,5,Cvision
OL,7,FConservatives leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Fsaid: "He needs to come to Parliament,
OL,9,Ftell us what he wants to do and face
OL,10,Fsome questions from MPs, the people
OL,11,Felected to hold the Government to
OL,12,Faccount.
OL,14,F"Giving speeches in Manchester and not
OL,15,Ftaking any questions is simply not
OL,16,Fgood enough."
OL,18,FReform UK's deputy leader Richard
OL,19,FTrice said: "No debate in Parliament.
OL,20,FNo scrutiny from MPs until September.
OL,21,FPower without accountability."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782816485
OL,3,CBurnham refuses to take journalists'
OL,4,Cquestions after speech setting out
OL,5,Cvision
OL,7,FBut Tony Blair's former spokesman
OL,8,FAlastair Campbell said it was a "good
OL,9,Fmove" for Burnham not to subject
OL,10,Fhimself to questions from the media.
OL,12,FHe said: "Speeches matter and when
OL,13,Fimportant should speak for themselves.
OL,15,F"If and when he becomes PM, Burnham
OL,16,Fwill be answerable to Parliament, not
OL,17,Fthe showbiz-style media coverage of
OL,18,Fpolitics."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
